title: Station.lua
content:
local station = peripheral.wrap("right")

local trainDocked = false
local trainDockedTime = 0
while true do

  if redstone.getInput("top") then
    if not trainDocked then
      trainDocked = true
      trainDockedTime = os.clock()
    end
    if os.clock()-trainDockedTime >= 2 then
      station.disassemble()
    end
  else
    trainDocked = false
  end

  sleep(0.05)
end

title: ComputerCraft Turtle Basement Digger (gravel fix))
content:
--dig block in front
function dig()
  while turtle.detect() do
    turtle.dig()
  end
end

function digUp()
  while turtle.detectUp() do
    turtle.digUp()
  end
end

--dig block in front and move forward
function digForward()
  dig()
  turtle.forward()
end

local tArgs = {...}
if #tArgs ~= 3 then
  print("Requires length, width, height")
  return
end

local x = tonumber(tArgs[1]) - 1
local y = tonumber(tArgs[2])
local z = tonumber(tArgs[3])

if x == nil or y == nil or z == nil then
  print("Invalid dimensions")
  return
end

if x < 0 or y < 0 or z < 0 then
  print("Invalid (negative) dimensions")
  return
end

local fuel = turtle.getFuelLevel()
local roomSize = x * y * z
while fuel < roomSize do
  if not turtle.refuel(1) then
    print("Not enough fuel")
    return
  end
end

local direction = true
for i = 1, z do
  for j = 1, y do
    for k = 1, x do
      digForward()
    end
    if j < y then
      if direction then
        turtle.turnRight()
        digForward()
        turtle.turnRight()
        direction = false
      else
        turtle.turnLeft()
        digForward()
        turtle.turnLeft()
        direction = true
      end
    end
  end
  if i < z then
    digUp()
    turtle.up()
    turtle.turnRight()
    turtle.turnRight() 
  end
end

if y % 2 == 0 then
  turtle.turnRight()
  for i = 1, y do
    turtle.forward()
  end
  turtle.turnRight()
else
  turtle.turnLeft()
  for i = 1, y do
    turtle.forward()
  end
  turtle.turnLeft()
  for i = 1, x do
    turtle.forward()
  end
  turtle.turnRight()
  turtle.turnRight()
end
for i = 1, z do
  turtle.down()
end

title: ClearArea
content:
--Area clear program
---takes x y z size as parameters
---assumes it is in bottom left back corner with chest behind itself

------------------------------------------------------------
--variables
local xPos = 0
local yPos = 0
local zPos = 0
local xSize
local ySize
local zSize
local facing = 1 --0 = +x,   1 = +z,   2 = -x,   3 = -z

------------------------------------------------------------
--functions

--check if inventory full
function inventoryFull()
  for i=1,16 do
    if turtle.getItemCount(i) == 0 then
      return false
    end
  end
  return true
end

--empty inventory
function unload()
  for i=1,16 do
    turtle.select(i)
    turtle.drop()
  end
end

--turn left
function turnLeft()
  turtle.turnLeft()
  facing = facing - 1
  if facing < 0 then
    facing = 3
  end
end

--turn right
function turnRight()
  turtle.turnRight()
  facing = facing + 1
  if facing > 3 then
    facing = 0
  end
end

--turn around
function turnAround()
  turnLeft()
  turnLeft()
end

--move forward
function forward()
  if turtle.forward() then
    if facing == 0 then
      xPos = xPos + 1
    elseif facing == 1 then
      zPos = zPos + 1
    elseif facing == 2 then
      xPos = xPos - 1
    elseif facing == 3 then
      zPos = zPos - 1
    end
    return true
  else
    return false
  end
end

--move back
function back()
  if turtle.back() then
    if facing == 0 then
      xPos = xPos - 1
    elseif facing == 1 then
      zPos = zPos - 1
    elseif facing == 2 then
      xPos = xPos + 1
    elseif facing == 3 then
      zPos = zPos + 1
    end
    return true
  else
    return false
  end
end

--move up
function up()
  if turtle.up() then
    yPos = yPos + 1
    return true
  else
    return false
  end
end

--move down
function down()
  if turtle.down() then
    yPos = yPos - 1
    return true
  else
    return false
  end
end

--dig block in front
function dig()
  while turtle.detect() do
    turtle.dig()
  end
end

--dig block above
function digUp()
  while turtle.detectUp() do
    turtle.digUp()
  end
end

--dig block below
function digDown()
  while turtle.detectDown() do
    turtle.digDown()
  end
end

--dig block in front and move forward
function digForward()
  dig()
  forward()
end

function face(dir)
    dir = dir % 4
    while facing ~= dir do
        turnLeft()
    end
end

--move to specified coordinates, if nil keep axis the same
function move(x, y, z)
    --order: y, x, z
    --y
    if y ~= nil then
        while yPos < y do
            up()
        end
        while yPos > y do
            down()
        end
    end

    --x
    if x ~= nil then
        if x > xPos then
            face(0)
            while xPos < x do
                digForward()
            end
        elseif x < xPos then
            face(2)
            while xPos > x do
                digForward()
            end
        end
    end

    --z
    if z ~= nil then
        if z > zPos then
            face(1)
            while zPos < z do
                digForward()
            end
        elseif z < zPos then
            face(3)
            while zPos > z do
                digForward()
            end
        end
    end
end

--dig out a layer on the y z plane
function digLayer()
    --dig out layer
    face(1)
    for y=1,ySize do
        for z=2, zSize do
            digForward()
        end
        digUp()
        up()
        turnAround()
    end
end

------------------------------------------------------------
--main program

--check if we have three arguments
if #arg ~= 3 then
  print("Usage: cleararea <x> <y> <z>")
  return
end

--get arguments
xSize = tonumber(arg[1])
ySize = tonumber(arg[2])
zSize = tonumber(arg[3])

--check if arguments are valid
if xSize == nil or ySize == nil or zSize == nil then
  print("Invalid arguments")
  return
end

--check if we have enough fuel
if turtle.getFuelLevel() < (xSize*ySize*zSize) then
  print("Not enough fuel")
  print("Need "..(xSize*ySize*zSize).." have "..turtle.getFuelLevel())
  return
end

--start digging
for x=1,xSize do
    digLayer()
    if inventoryFull() then
        move(0, 0, 0)
        face(3)
        unload()
        move(-x, 0, 0)
    end
    move(-x, 0, 0)
end

--return to start
move(0, 0, 0)
face(3)
unload()

print("Done")

title: openhud
content:
local sides = require("sides")
local event = require("event")
local com = require("component")
local serialization = require("serialization")

local default = {
    offsetX = 0,
    offsetY = 0,
    reactor = false,
    redstone = false,
    tankTritium = false,
    redstoneSide = false,
    laserAmplifier = false,
    tankDeuterium = false,
    glassesTerminal = false,
    inductionMatrix = false,
    laIgnitionEnergy = 1250000
}

local buttons = {}

local status = {
    maxEnergy = 0,
    maxCaseHeat = 0,
    imMaxStorage = 0,
    maxPlasmaHeat = 0,
    maxEnergyStored = 0,
    laMaxEnergyStored = 0
}

local statusbox = {}
statusbox.widgets = {}

local injectionRateWidget = {}

function initComponents()
    for address,type in pairs(component.list("glasses")) do
		if default.glassesTerminal == false then
			print("найденный терминал для очков "..address)
			default.glassesTerminal = component.proxy(address)
		else
			print("найден другой терминал для очков ("..address.."). будет использоваться первый.")
		end
	end

    for address,type in pairs(component.list("reactor_logic_adapter")) do
		if default.reactor == false then
			print("найден реактор "..address)
			default.reactor = component.proxy(address)
		else
			print("найден другой реактор ("..address.."). будет использован первый.")
		end
	end

    for address,type in pairs(component.list("laser_amplifier")) do
		if default.laserAmplifier == false then
			print("найден лазерный усилитель "..address)
			default.laserAmplifier = component.proxy(address)
		else
			print("найден другой лазерный усилитель ("..address.."). будет использован первый.")
		end
	end

    for address,type in pairs(component.list("redstone")) do
		if default.redstone == false then
			print("найден интерфейс redstone "..address)
			default.redstone = component.proxy(address)
		else
			print("нашел другой интерфейс redstone ("..address.."). будет использован первый.")
		end
	end

    for address,type in pairs(component.list("induction_matrix")) do
		if default.inductionMatrix == false then
			print("найденная индукционная матрица "..address)
			default.inductionMatrix = component.proxy(address)
		else
			print("нашел другую индукционную матрицу("..address.."). будет использован первая.")
		end
	end

    for address,type in pairs(component.list("_gas_tank")) do
        checkTank(address)
        os.sleep(0)
    end
end

function val2perc(val, maxVal)
	if(maxVal == 0) then return 0; end
	return (math.floor(0.5 + ((val/maxVal) * 100)*10)/10)
end

function readTankFull(address)
	local tank = component.proxy(address)
	return { 
        gas = tank.getGas().label, 
        amount = tank.getStoredGas(), 
        maxAmount = tank.getMaxGas(), 
        tankType = tank.type }
end

function readTankStorage(tank)
	return { 
        amount = tank.getStoredGas(), 
        maxAmount = tank.getMaxGas() 
    }
end

function checkTank(address)
	local tankData = readTankFull(address)
	if tankData.gas == nil then tankData.gas = "unknown"; end
	print("# found ".. tankData.tankType .. " with " .. tankData.amount .. "/" .. tankData.maxAmount .. " of " .. tankData.gas)	
	if string.match(tankData.gas, "deuterium") then
		print(" ... добавление резервуара с адресом " .. address)
		if default.tankDeuterium == false then
			default.tankDeuterium = component.proxy(address)
		else
			print("найдено более одного баллона с дейтериевым газом, используя первый найденный")
			print("задайте адрес в скрипте для использования определенного пользователем резервуара")
		end
	elseif string.match(tankData.gas, "tritium") then
		print(" ... добавление резервуара с адресом".. address)
		if default.tankTritium == false then
			default.tankTritium = component.proxy(address)
		else
			print("найдено более одного баллона с тритиевым газом, используя первый найденный")
			print("задайте адрес в скрипте для использования определенного пользователем резервуара")
		end
	end
end

require("term").clear()
print("\n# OpenHud starting...\n")
require("openglasses/open-hud")
offsetY = 60

initComponents()
glassesTerminal.removeAll()
initStatusBox()
initInjectionRateMenue(offsetX + 370, offsetY);

stopme = false
function stop()
	stopme=true
end

if tankDeuterium ~= false then hudDeuterium = addInfoHUD(10, 0, 100, 20, "Deuterium"); end
if tankTritium ~= false then hudTritium = addInfoHUD(10, 25, 100, 20, "Tritium"); end
hudProduction = addReactorHUD(10, 50, 100, 20, "Reactor")

addButton("ignite", offsetX + 10, offsetY + 75, 100, 20, ignite)

bI = addButton("[X]", 5, 5, 25, 25, stop)
--buttons[bI].widgets.box.addAutoTranslation(100, 0)
--buttons[bI].widgets.text.addAutoTranslation(100, 0)

--register event listeners and idle until user interrupts

function refreshAll()
	--update tank status
	updateTankHUD("Tritium", tankTritium, hudTritium)	
	updateTankHUD("Deuterium", tankDeuterium, hudDeuterium) 
		
	--update reactor production rate
	hudProduction[2].setText(formatNumber(MJ2RF(reactor.getProducing())).."RF/tick")	
		
	--update big status box
	updateStatusBox()
end

--updateEvent = event.timer(1, refreshAll, math.huge)

event.listen("interact_overlay", touchEvent)

print("\n# OpenHud loaded, close with [CTRL] + [C]")
--event.pull("interrupted")


event.listen("interrupted", stop)

while stopme == false do
	refreshAll()
end

-- cancel and ignore events
--event.cancel(updateEvent)
event.ignore("interact_overlay", touchEvent)
event.ignore("interrupted", stop)

-- remove all widgets from glasses
glassesTerminal.removeAll()

print("OpenHud closed\n")

title: snowybot completed
test main
content:
local modem = peripheral.find("modem") or error("No modem attached", 0)
modem.open(20)

local motor = peripheral.wrap("back")
local redstonePort = peripheral.wrap("top")


local DEBUG = true


local GRIDMULTX = 4
local GRIDMULTZ = 8


local currentPosition = {0,0,0}


local stickersEnabled = false


function split(pString, pPattern)
  local Table = {}  -- NOTE: use {n = 0} in Lua-5.0
  local fpat = "(.-)" .. pPattern
  local last_end = 1
  local s, e, cap = pString:find(fpat, 1)
  while s do
         if s ~= 1 or cap ~= "" then
        table.insert(Table,cap)
         end
         last_end = e+1
         s, e, cap = pString:find(fpat, last_end)
  end
  if last_end <= #pString then
         cap = pString:sub(last_end)
         table.insert(Table, cap)
  end
  return Table
end


function toggleStickers()
  redstonePort.setOutput("up",true)
  sleep(0.5)
  redstonePort.setOutput("up",false)
  sleep(0.5)

  stickersEnabled = not stickersEnabled

  if DEBUG then
    print("toggled stickers, state: " .. tostring(stickersEnabled))
  end
end

function resetOutputs()
  redstonePort.setOutput("west",false)
  redstone.setOutput("right",false)

  if DEBUG then
    print("reset outputs")
  end
end

function waitTilFinished()
  repeat sleep(0.1) until not motor.isRunning()
  sleep(1)

  if DEBUG then
    print("movement finished")
  end
end


function newMoveX(targetX)

  local movement = targetX-currentPosition[1]
  local movementType = 1
  if movement < 0 then
    movementType = -1
  end

  resetOutputs()
  redstonePort.setOutput("west",true)
  sleep(.5)
  if DEBUG then
    print("moving X")
  end
  motor.move(math.abs(movement),-movementType)
  currentPosition[1] = currentPosition[1]+movement
  waitTilFinished()

end
function newMoveY(targetY)

  local movement = targetY-currentPosition[2]
  local movementType = 1
  if movement < 0 then
    movementType = -1
  end

  resetOutputs()
  redstonePort.setOutput("west",true)
  redstone.setOutput("right",true)
  sleep(.5)
  if DEBUG then
    print("moving Y")
  end
  motor.move(math.abs(movement),movementType)
  currentPosition[2] = currentPosition[2]+movement
  waitTilFinished()

end
function newMoveZ(targetZ)

  local movement = targetZ-currentPosition[3]
  local movementType = 1
  if movement < 0 then
    movementType = -1
  end

  resetOutputs()
  sleep(.5)
  if DEBUG then
    print("moving Z")
  end
  motor.move(math.abs(movement),movementType)
  currentPosition[3] = currentPosition[3]+movement
  waitTilFinished()

end


function moveX(movement,direction)
  resetOutputs()
  redstonePort.setOutput("west",true)
  sleep(.5)
  if DEBUG then
    print("moving X")
  end
  motor.move(movement,-direction)
  currentPosition[1] = currentPosition[1]+(movement*-direction)
  waitTilFinished()
end

function moveZ(movement,direction)
  resetOutputs()
  sleep(.5)
  if DEBUG then
    print("moving Z")
  end
  motor.move(movement,direction)
  currentPosition[3] = currentPosition[3]+(movement*direction)
  waitTilFinished()
end

function moveY(movement,direction)
  resetOutputs()
  redstonePort.setOutput("west",true)
  redstone.setOutput("right",true)
  sleep(.5)
  if DEBUG then
    print("moving Y")
  end
  motor.move(movement,direction)
  currentPosition[2] = currentPosition[2]+(movement*direction)
  waitTilFinished()
end


function resetGantry()

  if not redstone.getInput("bottom") then
    moveY(9,-1)
  end

  while not redstone.getInput("bottom") do
    if not redstone.getInput("bottom") then
      moveX(6,-1)
    end
    if not redstone.getInput("bottom") then
      moveZ(6,-1)
    end
  end

  currentPosition = {0,0,0}

  if DEBUG then
    print("reset gantry")
  end

end


function moveToPoint(x,y,z)

  if DEBUG then
    print("moving to point: (".. tostring(x) .. ", " .. tostring(y) .. ", " .. tostring(z) .. ")")
  end

  newMoveX((x-1)*GRIDMULTX)
  newMoveZ((z-1)*GRIDMULTZ)
  newMoveY(y)

end


function grabContainer()

  if stickersEnabled then
    toggleStickers()
  end

  newMoveY(9)

  if not stickersEnabled then
    toggleStickers()
  end

  newMoveY(0)

end

function dropContainer()

  if not stickersEnabled then
    toggleStickers()
  end

  newMoveY(9)

  if stickersEnabled then
    toggleStickers()
  end

  newMoveY(0)

end


function grabContainerAt(x,z)

  moveToPoint(x,0,z)
  grabContainer()

end

function dropContainerAt(x,z)

  moveToPoint(x,0,z)
  dropContainer()

end

function moveContainerTo(x1,z1,x2,z2)

  grabContainerAt(x1,z1)
  dropContainerAt(x2,z2)

end

function checkSpaceAt(x,z,default)
  moveToPoint(x,0,z)

  newMoveY(9)

  local scanOutput = default or false
  if redstonePort.getInput("east") then
    scanOutput = true
  else
    scanOutput = false
  end

  newMoveY(0)

  return scanOutput
end


function printCurrentPosition()
  print(currentPosition[1])
  print(currentPosition[2])
  print(currentPosition[3])
end


resetGantry()

while true do

  if DEBUG then
    print("waiting")
  end

  local event, side, channel, replyChannel, message, distance
  repeat
    event, side, channel, replyChannel, message, distance = os.pullEvent("modem_message")
  until channel == 20

  local taskList = split(tostring(message),"-")
  local taskType = taskList[1]
  local args = taskList[2]

  if DEBUG then
    print("Task recieved: "..tostring(message))
    print("Task type: "..taskType)
    print("Task args: "..args)
  end
  if taskType == "SortAt" then
    if tonumber(args) ~= nil then
      currentXIndex = 6
      local availableX = checkSpaceAt(currentXIndex,tonumber(args))
      if not availableX then
        repeat
          currentXIndex = currentXIndex-1
          availableX = checkSpaceAt(currentXIndex,tonumber(args))
        until availableX or currentXIndex == 1
      end
      if availableX then
        moveContainerTo(9,2,currentXIndex,tonumber(args))
      else
        print("no space available")
      end
    end
  elseif taskType == "Deliver" then
    if tonumber(args) ~= nil then
      currentXIndex = 6
      local availableX = checkSpaceAt(currentXIndex,tonumber(args),true)
      if availableX then
        repeat
          currentXIndex = currentXIndex-1
          availableX = checkSpaceAt(currentXIndex,tonumber(args),true)
        until availableX == false or currentXIndex == 1
      end
      if not availableX then
        moveContainerTo(currentXIndex,tonumber(args),10,2)
      else
        print("no crates found")
      end
    end
  end

end

    scaleBoxText = "% Slap Button Scale" -- debug --
}

local FontList = {
    checkBoxFontObject = NumberFontNormalLargeYellow -- NumberFontNormalLargeYellow Game15Font
}

-- ===================================================================================================
-- ===================================================================================================
-- ===========================         global keybinding names          ===========================
-- ===================================================================================================
-- ===================================================================================================

BINDING_HEADER_SLAPDOWNTITLE = "- Slap Down -"
BINDING_NAME_SLAPDOWNTOGGLESLAPDOWNOPTIONS = "Toggle Slap Down Options"
BINDING_NAME_SLAPDOWNRUNSLAPDOWNFUNCTION = "Slap Down Function"
BINDING_NAME_SLAPDOWNRESTSLAPDOWNBUTTON = "Reset Slap Down Button"

-- ===================================================================================================
-- ===================================================================================================
-- ===========================         functions          ===========================
-- ===================================================================================================
-- ===================================================================================================

local function initialiseLists()
    if not SlapDownReasonList then
        SlapDownReasonList = {}
        SlapDownInsultList = {}
        SlapDownSettings = {
            showSlapDownButton = true,
            floatingButtonScale = 1
        }
    end
end

local function updateFailReasonList()
    FauxScrollFrame_Update(
        FailReasonListScrollFrame,
        #SlapDownReasonList,
        NumberList.scrollButtonNumber,
        NumberList.scrollButtonHeight
    )
    for index = 1, NumberList.scrollButtonNumber do
        local offset = index + FauxScrollFrame_GetOffset(FailReasonListScrollFrame)
        local button = FailReasonListScrollFrame.buttons[index]
        button:SetNormalFontObject(FontList.checkBoxFontObject)
        button:SetHighlightFontObject(FontList.checkBoxFontObject)
        button.index = offset
        if offset <= #SlapDownReasonList then
            button:SetText(SlapDownReasonList[offset])
            button:Show()
        else
            button:Hide()
        end
    end
end

local function updateFailInsultList()
    FauxScrollFrame_Update(
        FailInsultListScrollFrame,
        #SlapDownInsultList,
        NumberList.scrollButtonNumber,
        NumberList.scrollButtonHeight
    )
    for index = 1, NumberList.scrollButtonNumber do
        offset = index + FauxScrollFrame_GetOffset(FailInsultListScrollFrame)
        button = FailInsultListScrollFrame.buttons[index]
        button:SetNormalFontObject(FontList.checkBoxFontObject)
        button:SetHighlightFontObject(FontList.checkBoxFontObject)
        button.index = offset
        if offset <= #SlapDownInsultList then
            button:SetText(SlapDownInsultList[offset])
            button:Show()
        else
            button:Hide()
        end
    end
end

local function updateSlapDownButtonPercentage(scaleNumber)
    if scaleNumber >= 301 then -- if the entered number is too high
        scaleNumber = 300
    elseif scaleNumber <= 49 then -- if the entered number is too low
        scaleNumber = 50
    end
    saveScaleNumber = scaleNumber / 100
    ScaleSlapDownButtonEditBox:SetText(scaleNumber)
    SlapDownMagicButton:SetScale(saveScaleNumber)
    SlapDownSettings.floatingButtonScale = saveScaleNumber
end

-- ===================================================================================================
-- ===================================================================================================
-- ===========================         global functions for keybinds       ===========================
-- ===================================================================================================
-- ===================================================================================================

function SLAPDOWNTOGGLESLAPDOWNOPTIONS()
    if SettingsPanel:IsShown() then
        HideUIPanel(SettingsPanel)
    else
        InterfaceOptionsFrame_OpenToCategory("Slap Down")
    end
end

function SLAPDOWNRUNSLAPDOWNFUNCTION()
    if IsInRaid() or IsInGroup() then
        if #SlapDownReasonList > 0 and #SlapDownInsultList > 0 then
            math.random() -- sometimes random is not so random so lets kick start it to help
            randomReasonString = math.random(1, #SlapDownReasonList)
            reasonString = (SlapDownReasonList[randomReasonString])

            math.random()
            randomInsultString = math.random(1, #SlapDownInsultList)
            insultString = (SlapDownInsultList[randomInsultString])

            numMembers = GetNumGroupMembers()
            math.random()
            randomNumber = math.random(1, numMembers)
            playerName = GetRaidRosterInfo(randomNumber)

            messageString = (playerName .. joinString1 .. reasonString .. joinString2 .. insultString)

            SendChatMessage(
                messageString,
                IsInGroup(LE_PARTY_CATEGORY_INSTANCE) and "INSTANCE_CHAT" or IsInRaid() and "RAID" or "PARTY"
            )
        else
            print(StringList.failMissingPhraseString)
        end
    else
        print(StringList.failNotInRaid)
    end
end

function SLAPDOWNRESTSLAPDOWNBUTTON()
    SlapDownMagicButton:ClearAllPoints()
    SlapDownMagicButton:SetPoint("CENTER", 0, 200)
    SlapDownMagicButton:Show()
    SlapDownSettings.showSlapDownButton = false
    updateSlapDownButtonPercentage(100)
end

-- ===================================================================================================
-- ===================================================================================================
-- ===========================         slash commands          ===========================
-- ===================================================================================================
-- ===================================================================================================

SLASH_SLAPDOWNTOGGLESLAPDOWNOPTIONS1 = "/SlapDownOptions"
function SlashCmdList.SLAPDOWNTOGGLESLAPDOWNOPTIONS(msg, editbox)
    SLAPDOWNTOGGLESLAPDOWNOPTIONS()
end

SLASH_SLAPDOWNRUNSLAPDOWNFUNCTION1 = "/SlapDown"
function SlashCmdList.SLAPDOWNRUNSLAPDOWNFUNCTION(msg, editbox)
    SLAPDOWNRUNSLAPDOWNFUNCTION()
end

SLASH_SLAPDOWNRESTSLAPDOWNBUTTON1 = "/SlapDownPos"
function SlashCmdList.SLAPDOWNRESTSLAPDOWNBUTTON(msg, editbox)
    SLAPDOWNRESTSLAPDOWNBUTTON()
end

-- ===================================================================================================
-- ===================================================================================================
-- ===========================         frames          ===========================
-- ===================================================================================================
-- ===================================================================================================

local SlapDownInterfaceFrame = CreateFrame("Frame")
SlapDownInterfaceFrame.name = "Slap Down"
SlapDownInterfaceFrame:SetScript(
    "OnEvent",
    function(self, event, ...)
        if event == "PLAYER_LOGIN" then
            print(ColourList.colourText .. " *** " .. addonName .. " - " .. versionNumber .. " Loaded *** \n") -- Load Message
            initialiseLists()
            updateFailReasonList()
            updateFailInsultList()

            if SlapDownSettings.showSlapDownButton then
                ShowSlapDownButtonCheckBox:SetChecked(true)
                SlapDownMagicButton:Show()
            else
                ShowSlapDownButtonCheckBox:SetChecked(false)
                SlapDownMagicButton:Hide()
            end

            print(SlapDownSettings.floatingButtonScale * 100) -- debug --
            updateSlapDownButtonPercentage(SlapDownSettings.floatingButtonScale * 100)
            --  ScaleSlapDownButtonEditBox:SetText(SlapDownSettings.floatingButtonScale * 100)

            SlapDownMagicButton:SetScale(SlapDownSettings.floatingButtonScale)
        elseif event == "PLAYER_ENTERING_WORLD" or event == "GROUP_FORMED" or event == "GROUP_JOINED" then
            print(event, UnitInAnyGroup("player"), IsInRaid(), IsInGroup(), IsInInstance()) -- debug --
            if UnitInAnyGroup("player") or IsInRaid() or IsInGroup() or IsInInstance() then
                SlapDownMagicButton:Show()
            end
        elseif event == "GROUP_LEFT" then
            if UnitInAnyGroup("player") or IsInRaid() or IsInGroup() or IsInInstance() then
                SlapDownMagicButton:Show()
            elseif SlapDownSettings.showSlapDownButton then
                SlapDownMagicButton:Show()
            else
                SlapDownMagicButton:Hide()
            end
        end
    end
)
SlapDownInterfaceFrame:RegisterEvent("PLAYER_LOGIN") -- fires when a player logs in or reloads
SlapDownInterfaceFrame:RegisterEvent("PLAYER_ENTERING_WORLD") -- fires when the player sees a loading screen
SlapDownInterfaceFrame:RegisterEvent("GROUP_FORMED") -- fires when the player starts a group
SlapDownInterfaceFrame:RegisterEvent("GROUP_JOINED") -- fires when the player joins a group
SlapDownInterfaceFrame:RegisterEvent("GROUP_LEFT") -- fires when the player leaves a group
InterfaceOptions_AddCategory(SlapDownInterfaceFrame)

local SlapDownBanner = CreateFrame("Frame", "SlapDownBanner", SlapDownInterfaceFrame)
SlapDownBanner:SetSize(NumberList.bannerBoxSize, NumberList.bannerBoxSize)
SlapDownBanner:SetScale(NumberList.bannerScale)
SlapDownBanner:SetPoint("TOP", 0, 0)
SlapDownBanner.Texture = SlapDownBanner:CreateTexture(nil, "BACKGROUND")
SlapDownBanner.Texture:SetPoint("TOP", 0, 0)
SlapDownBanner.Texture:SetTexture(ImageList.sdBanner)

local ShowSlapDownButtonCheckBox =
    CreateFrame("CheckButton", "ShowSlapDownButtonCheckBox", SlapDownInterfaceFrame, "UICheckButtonTemplate")
ShowSlapDownButtonCheckBox:SetPoint(
    "TOPRIGHT",
    SlapDownInterfaceFrame,
    "TOPLEFT",
    NumberList.checkBoxSideGap,
    NumberList.checkBoxTopGap
)
ShowSlapDownButtonCheckBox.text:SetFontObject(FontList.checkBoxFontObject)
ShowSlapDownButtonCheckBox.text:SetText(StringList.checkBoxText)
ShowSlapDownButtonCheckBox:SetScript(
    "OnClick",
    function()
        if SlapDownSettings.showSlapDownButton then
            SlapDownSettings.showSlapDownButton = false
            SlapDownMagicButton:Hide()
        else
            SlapDownSettings.showSlapDownButton = true
            SlapDownMagicButton:Show()
        end
    end
)

local ScaleSlapDownButtonEditBox =
    CreateFrame("EditBox", "ScaleSlapDownButtonEditBox", SlapDownInterfaceFrame, "ChatConfigBoxTemplate")
ScaleSlapDownButtonEditBox:SetPoint("LEFT", ShowSlapDownButtonCheckBox, "RIGHT", NumberList.scaleBoxGap, 0)
ScaleSlapDownButtonEditBox:SetFontObject(FontList.checkBoxFontObject)
ScaleSlapDownButtonEditBox:SetNumeric(true)
ScaleSlapDownButtonEditBox:SetSize(NumberList.percentageTextBoxWidth, NumberList.percentageTextBoxHeight)
ScaleSlapDownButtonEditBox:SetMaxLetters(3)
ScaleSlapDownButtonEditBox:SetAutoFocus()
-- ScaleSlapDownButtonEditBox:SetText("") -- debug --
ScaleSlapDownButtonEditBox:SetJustifyH("CENTER")
ScaleSlapDownButtonEditBox:SetScript(
    "OnEnterPressed",
    function(self)
        scaleNumber = tonumber(ScaleSlapDownButtonEditBox:GetText())
        self:ClearFocus()
        updateSlapDownButtonPercentage(scaleNumber)
    end
)

ScaleSlapDownButtonEditBox.Text = ScaleSlapDownButtonEditBox:CreateFontString("ScaleSlapDownButtonEditBoxText")
ScaleSlapDownButtonEditBoxText:SetPoint("LEFT", ScaleSlapDownButtonEditBox, "RIGHT")
ScaleSlapDownButtonEditBoxText:SetFontObject(FontList.checkBoxFontObject)
ScaleSlapDownButtonEditBoxText:SetText(StringList.scaleBoxText)

local FailReasonLabelBox = CreateFrame("Frame", "FailReasonLabelBox", SlapDownInterfaceFrame)
FailReasonLabelBox:SetPoint("LEFT", SlapDownInterfaceFrame, "LEFT", NumberList.labelSideGap, NumberList.labelTopGap)
FailReasonLabelBox:SetSize(NumberList.labelSizeX, NumberList.labelSizeY)
FailReasonLabelBox.Text = FailReasonLabelBox:CreateFontString("FailReasonLabelBoxText")
FailReasonLabelBoxText:SetPoint("LEFT", FailReasonLabelBox)
FailReasonLabelBoxText:SetFontObject(FontList.checkBoxFontObject)
FailReasonLabelBoxText:SetText(StringList.failReasonLabelText)

local EnterFailReasonEditBox =
    CreateFrame("EditBox", "EnterFailReasonEditBox", SlapDownInterfaceFrame, "ChatConfigBoxTemplate")
EnterFailReasonEditBox:SetPoint("TOPLEFT", FailReasonLabelBox, "BOTTOMLEFT")
EnterFailReasonEditBox:SetFontObject(FontList.checkBoxFontObject)
EnterFailReasonEditBox:SetAutoFocus()
EnterFailReasonEditBox:SetJustifyH("LEFT")
EnterFailReasonEditBox:SetSize(NumberList.failEditBoxWidth, NumberList.failEditBoxHeight)
EnterFailReasonEditBox:SetTextInsets(10, 10, 0, 0)
EnterFailReasonEditBox:SetScript(
    "OnEnterPressed",
    function(self)
        failReasonString = tostring(EnterFailReasonEditBox:GetText())
        if failReasonString ~= "" then
            table.insert(SlapDownReasonList, 1, failReasonString)
            self:ClearFocus()
            self:SetText("")
            updateFailReasonList()
        else
            print("empty string")
        end
    end
)

local FailListReasonScrollParent =
    CreateFrame("Frame", "FailListReasonScrollParent", SlapDownInterfaceFrame, "ChatConfigBoxTemplate")
FailListReasonScrollParent:SetSize(NumberList.failEditBoxWidth, NumberList.scrollFrameHeight)
FailListReasonScrollParent:SetPoint("TOPLEFT", EnterFailReasonEditBox, "BOTTOMLEFT")

local FailReasonListScrollFrame =
    CreateFrame("ScrollFrame", "FailReasonListScrollFrame", FailListReasonScrollParent, "FauxScrollFrameTemplate")
FailReasonListScrollFrame:SetPoint("TOPLEFT", 0, -8)
FailReasonListScrollFrame:SetPoint("BOTTOMRIGHT", -30, 8)
FailReasonListScrollFrame:SetScript(
    "OnVerticalScroll",
    function(self, offset)
        FauxScrollFrame_OnVerticalScroll(self, offset, NumberList.scrollButtonHeight, updateFailReasonList)
    end
)

FailReasonListScrollFrame.buttons = {}
for index = 1, NumberList.scrollButtonNumber do
    FailReasonListScrollFrame.buttons[index] =
        CreateFrame("Button", "$parentbtn" .. index, FailListReasonScrollParent, "OptionsListButtonTemplate")
    local button = FailReasonListScrollFrame.buttons[index]
    button:SetSize(NumberList.failEditBoxWidth, NumberList.scrollButtonHeight)
    button:SetPoint("TOPLEFT", 8, -(index - 1) * NumberList.scrollButtonHeight - 8)
    button:SetScript(
        "OnClick",
        function(self, button)
            if button == "RightButton" then
                table.remove(SlapDownReasonList, self.index)
                updateFailReasonList()
            end
        end
    )
end

local FailInsultLabelBox = CreateFrame("Frame", "FailInsultLabelBox", SlapDownInterfaceFrame)
FailInsultLabelBox:SetPoint("BOTTOMLEFT", FailListReasonScrollParent, "TOPLEFT", 0, NumberList.failTopGap)
FailInsultLabelBox:SetSize(NumberList.labelSizeX, NumberList.labelSizeY)
FailInsultLabelBox.Text = FailInsultLabelBox:CreateFontString("FailInsultLabelBoxText")
FailInsultLabelBoxText:SetPoint("LEFT", FailInsultLabelBox)
FailInsultLabelBoxText:SetFontObject(FontList.checkBoxFontObject)
FailInsultLabelBoxText:SetText(StringList.failInsultLabelText)

local EnterFailInsultEditBox =
    CreateFrame("EditBox", "EnterFailInsultEditBox", SlapDownInterfaceFrame, "ChatConfigBoxTemplate")
EnterFailInsultEditBox:SetPoint("TOPLEFT", FailInsultLabelBox, "BOTTOMLEFT")
EnterFailInsultEditBox:SetFontObject(FontList.checkBoxFontObject)
EnterFailInsultEditBox:SetAutoFocus()
EnterFailInsultEditBox:SetJustifyH("LEFT")
EnterFailInsultEditBox:SetSize(NumberList.failEditBoxWidth, NumberList.failEditBoxHeight)
EnterFailInsultEditBox:SetTextInsets(10, 10, 0, 0)
EnterFailInsultEditBox:SetScript(
    "OnEnterPressed",
    function(self)
        failInsultString = tostring(EnterFailInsultEditBox:GetText())
        if failInsultString ~= "" then
            table.insert(SlapDownInsultList, 1, failInsultString)
            self:ClearFocus()
            self:SetText("")
            updateFailInsultList()
        else
            print("empty string")
        end
    end
)

local FailListInsultScrollParent =
    CreateFrame("Frame", "FailListInsultScrollParent", SlapDownInterfaceFrame, "ChatConfigBoxTemplate")
FailListInsultScrollParent:SetSize(NumberList.failEditBoxWidth, NumberList.scrollFrameHeight)
FailListInsultScrollParent:SetPoint("TOPLEFT", EnterFailInsultEditBox, "BOTTOMLEFT")

local FailInsultListScrollFrame =
    CreateFrame("ScrollFrame", "FailInsultListScrollFrame", FailListInsultScrollParent, "FauxScrollFrameTemplate")
FailInsultListScrollFrame:SetPoint("TOPLEFT", 0, -8)
FailInsultListScrollFrame:SetPoint("BOTTOMRIGHT", -30, 8)
FailInsultListScrollFrame:SetScript(
    "OnVerticalScroll",
    function(self, offset)
        FauxScrollFrame_OnVerticalScroll(self, offset, NumberList.scrollButtonHeight, updateFailInsultList)
    end
)

FailInsultListScrollFrame.buttons = {}
for index = 1, NumberList.scrollButtonNumber do
    FailInsultListScrollFrame.buttons[index] =
        CreateFrame("Button", "$parentbtn" .. index, FailListInsultScrollParent, "OptionsListButtonTemplate")
    local button = FailInsultListScrollFrame.buttons[index]
    button:SetSize(NumberList.failEditBoxWidth, NumberList.scrollButtonHeight)
    button:SetPoint("TOPLEFT", 8, -(index - 1) * NumberList.scrollButtonHeight - 8)
    button:SetScript(
        "OnClick",
        function(self, button)
            if button == "RightButton" then
                table.remove(SlapDownInsultList, self.index)
                updateFailInsultList()
            end
        end
    )
end

local SlapDownMagicButton = CreateFrame("Button", "SlapDownMagicButton", UIParent)
SlapDownMagicButton:SetSize(NumberList.slapDownMagicButtonSize, NumberList.slapDownMagicButtonSize)
SlapDownMagicButton:ClearAllPoints()
SlapDownMagicButton:SetPoint("CENTER", 0, 200)
SlapDownMagicButton:SetNormalTexture(ImageList.sdButton)
SlapDownMagicButton:SetHighlightTexture(ImageList.sdButtonH, "BLEND")
SlapDownMagicButton:SetMovable(true)
SlapDownMagicButton:SetClampedToScreen(true)
SlapDownMagicButton:RegisterForDrag("MiddleButton")
SlapDownMagicButton:SetScript("OnDragStart", SlapDownMagicButton.StartMoving)
SlapDownMagicButton:SetScript("OnDragStop", SlapDownMagicButton.StopMovingOrSizing)
SlapDownMagicButton:RegisterForClicks("RightButtonUp", "LeftButtonUp")
SlapDownMagicButton:SetToplevel(true)
SlapDownMagicButton:SetScript(
    "OnClick",
    function(self, button)
        if button == "LeftButton" then
            SLAPDOWNRUNSLAPDOWNFUNCTION()
        elseif button == "RightButton" then
            SLAPDOWNTOGGLESLAPDOWNOPTIONS()
        end
    end
)

content:
#!/usr/bin/env zsh
# usage: greview <default_branch>
# example:
#       git checkout branch_to_review
#       greview master

base=${1:-master}
other=$(git rev-parse --abbrev-ref HEAD)

files=($(git diff --name-only ${base}..${other} | tr '\n' ' ' 2>/dev/null))
PROMPT3="select [x to exit]: "

while true; do
    select file in ${files[@]}; do
        case $file in
            *)
                if [[ "${REPLY}" =~ "^[0-9]+$" ]] ; then
                    file=${file/% \[x\]/}
                    if [ $REPLY -le $#files ] ; then
                        git difftool -t vimdiff ${base}..${other} ${file} 2>/dev/null
                        files[$REPLY]="${file} [x]"
                    fi
                    break
                elif [ "${REPLY}" = "x" ] ; then
                    echo "done..."
                    exit 0
                else
                    echo "invalid input: $REPLY, retry"
                fi
                ;;
        esac
    done
done

title: Ordinal numbers for python
content:
def add_number_suffix(n: int) -> str:
    """Adds suffix to passed in number, ie 1 becomes 1st, 13 becomes 13th....
    :param int number to add suffix
    : returns str
    """
    if 4 <= n <= 20 or 24 <= n % 100 <= 30:  # teens
        suffix = "th"
    else:
        suffix = {1: 'st', 2: 'nd', 3: 'rd'}.get(n % 10, 'th')
    return f'{n}{suffix}'
